    <scopecontent id="aspace_hzc212261n520as02127999687044">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>A transcript of a monologue given by Ernst Halberstadt 1985 Mar. 18. Halberstadt relates his memories of working in New York for Ezra Winter and Diego Rivera on the Radio City Music Hall murals, describing his contributions to the paintings and his working methods.</p>
    </scopecontent>
